<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<!-- @import "head" -->
<body>
  <!-- @import "header" -->
<main>
  <div class="history-banner">
    <img src="src/assets/img/OurHistory.png" alt="Wall lamp">
  </div>

  <h1>Our History</h1>

  <section class="elegance">
    <figure><img src="src/assets/img/CarvedArmchair.png" alt="Carved green armchair in a red room"></figure>
      <div class="history">
        <h2>Where history meets elegance</h2>
          <p>Since 1982, Héritage has been a sanctuary for the world's finest antiques and decorative arts. We believe that true luxury lies not in the new, but in the enduring beauty of objects that have witnessed history unfold. Today, HÉRITAGE continues this legacy with the same dedication to excellence that defined our founding. Our expert team travels across Europe and beyond, meticulously selecting pieces that embody exceptional craftsmanship, provenance, and artistic merit. From Baroque grandeur to Art Nouveau fluidity, each acquisition represents a chapter in the ongoing narrative of human creativity.</p>
      </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values">
    <h2>Our values</h2>
      <p>The principles that guide everything we do</p>
        <div class="values_list">
          <div class="authenticity">
            <figure><img src="src/assets/svg/Badge.svg" alt="Badge">
              <figcaption>Badge icon</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p class="authenticity-description">Every piece is meticulously verified for provenance and authenticity by our expert team.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="passion">
            <figure><img src="src/assets/svg/Passion.svg" alt="Passion">
              <figcaption>Passion icon</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p class="passion-description">Our love for history and craftsmanship drives everything we do, from acquisition to curation.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="integrity">
            <figure><img src="src/assets/svg/Shield.svg" alt="Shield">
              <figcaption>Shield icon</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p class="integrity-description">We uphold the highest ethical standards in all our dealings, ensuring trust and transparency.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="heritage">
            <figure><img src="src/assets/svg/Heritage.svg" alt="Heritage icon">
              <figcaption>Heritage icon</figcaption>
            </figure>
            <p class="heritage-description">We preserve cultural legacies, connecting the past with collectors who appreciate timeless beauty.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
  </section>

  <section class="journey">
    <figure><img src="src/assets/img/Crystal-Chandelier.png" alt="Chandelier on the ceiling"></figure>
      <div class="our-journey">
        <h2>Our journey</h2>
        <p>Over four decades, Héritage has grown from a single gallery to a cornerstone of European antique curation. Each milestone represents our commitment to preserving cultural heritage and serving discerning collectors worldwide.</p>
        <div>
          <h3>1982</h3>
          <p>Héritage founded in Lisbon by Isabella Monteiro</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3>1995</h3>
          <p>Expanded to include European auction services</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3>2005</h3>
          <p>Opened dedicated restoration workshop</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3>2012</h3>
          <p>Established partnerships with major European museums</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3>2020</h3>
          <p>Launched digital catalogue and virtual viewings</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3>2026</h3>
          <p>Celebrating over 40 years of curatorial excellence</p>
        </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <section class="team">
    <h2>Meet our team</h2>
    <p>Passionate experts dedicated to preserving history</p>
    <div class="our-team">
      <div class="member1">
        <figure><img src="src/assets/img/Isabella.png" alt="Isabella"></figure>
        <p class="position">Founder & Chief Curator</p>
        <p>With over 35 years of experience in European decorative arts, Isabella founded HÉRITAGE to share her passion for preserving history.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="member2">
        <figure><img src="src/assets/img/Rafael.png" alt="Rafael"></figure>
        <p class="position">Senior Acquisitions Director</p>
        <p>Rafael travels extensively across Europe, sourcing exceptional pieces and building relationships with collectors and estates.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="member3">
        <figure><img src="src/assets/img/Pedro.png" alt="Shield"></figure>
        <p class="position">Head of Authentication & Research</p>
        <p>A renowned art historian, Dr. Santos ensures every piece meets our rigorous standards of authenticity and historical significance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
  <!-- @import "footer" -->

</body>
</html>